Title: Canonical and Functional Schrodinger Quantization of Two--Dimensional

Dilaton GravityAuthors: S. Cassemiro F. F. and Victor O. Rivelles

Comments: 12 pages, revtex Minor corrections

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B452 (1999) 234-239

We discuss the relation between canonical and Schrodinger quantization of theCGHS model. We also discuss the situation when background charges are added tocancel the Virasoro anomaly. New physical states are found when the square ofthe background charges vanishes.